name_for_human: Generate Image Condition On Canny Image
description_for_human: useful when you want to generate a new real image from both the user description and a canny image.
description_for_model: useful when you want to generate a new real image from both the user description and a canny image. like: generate a real image of a object or something from this canny image, or generate a new real image of a object or something from this edge image. The input to this tool should be image path and the user description.
